# England 集群常用命令：
# 1. 主控机启动协调器：python run.py cluster coordinator
# 2. 任意 worker 机启动本机池：python run.py cluster start-pools
# 3. 提交英国全部来源：python run.py cluster submit England
# 4. 产出交付：python run.py cluster produce day2

